    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Caps worn underneath other headwear, often plain, and not intended to be seen, but some exhibiting embroidered or jewelled borders. These have been made in a variety of materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
